      <title>麦格理警告称，由于印度尼西亚的障碍，镍可能会出现赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/nickel-may-flip-to-deficit-on-indonesia-hurdles-macquarie-warns</link>
